arts.ttl: Stuttgart swat Regensburg aside to reach Pokal last eight
arts.sum: With only one win in their last six games, VfB Stuttgart were hopeful of a turn in fortunes against DfB Pokal opponents Jahn Regensburg tonight. The 2.Bundesliga side put up a fight but ultimately succumbed to a 3-0 defeat.

arts.ttl: Bredlow set for rare Stuttgart start
arts.sum: VfB Stuttgart coach Sebastian Hoeness has confirmed that Fabian Bredlow will make a rare start against SSV Jahn Regensburg in the DFB-Pokal.

arts.ttl: Preview: Jahn Regensburg vs. Stuttgart - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Tuesday's DFB-Pokal clash between Jahn Regensburg and Stuttgart, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.
